sequenceDiagram
    participant P1 as Client P1
    participant S as Relay Server
    participant P2 as Client P2

    P1->>S: create_room + version handshake
    P2->>S: join_room + version handshake
    S-->>P1: room_joined
    S-->>P2: room_joined

    P1->>S: loadout_commit
    P2->>S: loadout_commit
    S-->>P1: run_start(seed, dataPackHash, inputDelay)
    S-->>P2: run_start(seed, dataPackHash, inputDelay)

    loop Every 2-3 frames
        P1->>S: input_batch(baseFrame, inputs)
        P2->>S: input_batch(baseFrame, inputs)
        S-->>P1: relay P2 input_batch
        S-->>P2: relay P1 input_batch
    end

    loop Every 120 frames
        P1->>S: hash_report(frame, hash)
        P2->>S: hash_report(frame, hash)
    end

    Note over P1,P2: 灵气经验满，进入 insight_pause
    P1->>S: insight_decision(reroll/choose)
    P2->>S: insight_decision(reroll/choose)
    S-->>P1: ordered_room_event(serverDecisionSeq)
    S-->>P2: ordered_room_event(serverDecisionSeq)
    Note over P1,P2: 双方选择完成，同一 resumeFrame 继续
